ame \"supplier only when absent\" suggests a different approach. To minimize duplication, I could remove tags merging. I’ll also want to incorporate the assertThat method for integer checks to make the tests clearer.", "thinkingSignature": "{\"id\":\"rs_0f593d492f4fd13a0169fd0397cbc0819cb677fa170f713223\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABp_QOoFbeUMKZsHIOapDI_J9RN1CJ-BehG3gHC8iJhVbYOe_3tqoO534hKeptvuRITw3QXIAo5yfgW1h8lb-iYGCM6D4k3juNYzmy-RQ7RsOKY9VlV9-UaHJeHrRkhKMCnA5vAZJ_3l467qu_pqy3Ma-sDQZGGbNHnmrcNqH65OUF9FJzcE-RvnqZJ9Oqbmky-0xp1_b5kN5FiYIaKzAv0c7cBJKO6xmIgay7dGV3OjBXzOpr3nj8Q1ykQlQ_AYWlPAbctqQMGt-38uBsOt6SzSGbLIwXkoE3warlfVNobRmrB_KytdvZo1C2wUVxFX-z10ITro4BUMWjHpI73beuITls0_EHZ_gL6ZLdyhGp9EYvFInT5KfyvwhGz_S0ikfBW0zE2UgERQLokFuhif3hoK_5OZH9kSpDNSSLr37oHfLk8g2soEQHtVxb7o75GZPcw1ksKSVb-w_ptpyynQ_O0hudj_drKAvRrid1wl5YVeaOMMfTWPRtudhkdiQLU98EcPauRSDpbt4yhMSLAS0unQjMbNhCAsj7ZwNxoYRF2Qx5YoPxKy2bmO6oOb5PFmtFiU8xv9RnaYRsEahSywgSJkKh1oEhdu9Q-FJrbDAGoyrHktv5raSwtrWcbrPSMmLfAfcQvIHMMLY31yw3Tv2GDjBTTBiUH-xyAe7jiymP2Q8hXr69shu7lt2p54qwXTDDNvAX43Mz_GPkzDt9PPQcp0KdZYrEI1AQ6_qDNaPwJxFtwySfyrIbCMQFWAMbGv1R0jmEHUy42t0P3xGEQNqOBDKBudXGElFVvex2ld4PJlTCBSVgj035yVNV87q17jQCnQnzyvKqcdqytzDPPLvQ0IFEALeJZVaU3IEMxAHOZUYNhYxhzI5gWGRfYDWbFN4VVzTvIjubDaa6SH8QmWXk6_nd4tewkpRaq5fMz_n6ipZg5aauFmCMzKWmAt67mk-JJbHriHQIvl12Yk5XHifBqeISbFCzOSP65S27Paxyq_ULpXXymV9Ec8gAcwJi8Dt20vmNhUI7FoPMxCRQ9xAWVkK1acggNAUBo-rSQLohZYdejDBJY-VeB7IifzACNmcKLKh_aCYzwkqgTePgUeBO_j58OQWByT1fTlRSdfdVvVDU_K51mb6YklmyYZ4ZvLOVSa0lp57l_Tdaw6o-xRbwQT3g--_4JU_WbeQ_5E0v_6PkUK5fsge_Ihk7lM_vR60hyJ_Ahd0O4HeEiCdtf7mHGzCC-DtxwnNa6B-mwDqea7O8pA_QiTa3G8pms5gHIGg67j5KPk8Fvc9Omg5W92FX6AMwtZYgk3BH_a0mlHuzF6TtAkp7oC0pxP8-yOUNTIbrxGFRk5bqYZtAnGNiFezgJs1MmlRZ_xhzJfG_Oenil64etgLx1jKqI7b9SHfUjQD4IEyXrQ65BdFvKpmkVmVL0Eq1-Ccbjbz4TKl_74Y6HcoaTcFup5whk-9_--SFQh6cZl5bo4G8FSdOgs7vEfx2xoVRFez3K4DUiOR43f6xYp3IHC-wi_TLXqCdHC3dkiahnE17O95Js_ZE-c-3-XIBcRYqhjnz5wGLSGZBaEWHGdWUYeJTle7xM6YC4AkmX7dzGPX3qqt1bjTCdTVBmEQ64OCb3wyHb6xh2ox34I5